items.title: Body Language and Non-Verbal Cues: Your valuable guide
items.headline: Learn how to easily recognize and use nonverbal cues in your in everyday life - everything from Attraction to Deception
objectives_summary: This course shares knowledge about interpreting important non-verbal cues that occurs unconsciously. It gives a clear understanding of body language and what it says about you and others. We look at effective ways to use and recognise important non-verbal cues for dating, lie-detection, stress-indicators and involuntary actions that occur during conversations. Learning to read particular cues can greatly assist you when conducting interviews, assessing mistrust and interpret information people are giving about themselves. What people say and the truth are often a contradiction.
